### Create a new Description
POST http://localhost:3000/api/descriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Description for electronics shipment"
}

### Get all Descriptions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/descriptions

### Get a Description by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/descriptions/1

### Update a Description by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/descriptions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description for electronics shipment"
}

### Delete a Description by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/descriptions/1
